* Paludis

Add a new config file under /etc/paludis/repositories called scala.conf

>>>
location = ${ROOT}/PATH/TO/OVERLAY
sync = svn+http://lampsvn.epfl.ch/svn-repos/scala/scala-tool-support/trunk/src/gentoo
master_repository = gentoo
format = ebuild
names_cache = ${location}/.cache/names
write_cache = /var/cache/paludis/metadata
<<<

